                      /
                      <span>4</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2000-05-24</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>If you're a history fan, check this book out. It gives the reader a good overview of a subject they most likely havn't read anything on before. Ill be reading more of Cassons books after this, I hope they are as enjoyable.</span>
                  
              
